                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - B
                   ====================================

                                Bounty Bob
                                ==========


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Lives = x" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(50155,255)"}               50155,x (x= 1-255)

                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).

                         I cannot get this POKE to work. However, I have
                         left it here in case it works for some "other"
                         version of the game.
